<br>
Target the mob on me, step close to pet, /pet backoff, /pet attack (think I'm just gonna add /pet backoff to my attack hotkey now that I think about it). Sometimes it takes a few tries, but it will normally get the pet on the add eventually. Obviously it will be harder to do when the pet is on a quick hitter, but it has saved me a gate or three already.<br>
